import React from "react" import "./ProfileDetails.css" function ProfileDetails({ profile }){ return (
  • Name: {profile.name}
  • Age: {profile.age}
  • Phone: {profile.phone}
  • Email: {profile.email}
  • Address: {profile.address}
  • Freelance: {profile.freelance}
  • Github: {profile.github}
) } export { ProfileDetails }
